  <!--
    Iconography — Lucide subset path geometries.
    Per project_design_guide.md §3.

    Lucide source (ISC license): https://lucide.dev. All icons are on a
    24x24 viewBox; consumers render them as <Path Data="{StaticResource
    Icon.X}" Stroke="{DynamicResource OnSurfaceDefaultBrush}"
    StrokeThickness="1.5" StrokeStartLineCap="Round" .../> so theme swap
    re-tints the stroke without rebuilding visuals.

    Brand logomark lives in assets/logo.png (+ logo.ico for shell
    surfaces) and is consumed via pack URI in App.LoadEmbeddedTrayIcon
    + the SettingsWindow sidebar — earlier vector geometries are gone.

    Adding a new icon? (1) drop the StreamGeometry below alphabetically
    inside its section, (2) register the key in the
    LucideIconKeys array of ThemeDictionaryTests so the snapshot test
    asserts presence.
  -->

